videos.description: QB Tyree Jackson rushes up the middle on a draw play and blows past the Army defense to give Buffalo a 10-7 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Jackson rushes for 75-yard Buffalo TD) 2017/09/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jackson rushes for 75-yard Buffalo TD

videos.description: QB Tyree Jackson connects with WR Antonio Nunn who burns the defense for a 48-yard touchdown to give Buffalo a 17-7 lead against Army.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Nunn catches 48-yard TD for Buffalo) 2017/09/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Nunn catches 48-yard TD for Buffalo

videos.description: Army caps off a 16-play drive with a 1-yard touchdown by RB Darnell Woolfolk to cut into Buffalo's lead and make the score 17-14.
videos.headline: Army pushes through 1-yard TD

videos.description: With 2:28 left in the game, Army runs a fake punt on fourth down for 15-yards as Army comes back to beat Buffalo 21-17.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Army fakes punt to seal victory) 2017/09/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Army fakes punt to seal victory
